SUMMARY:African Arts in the Park Cultural Festival
LOCATION:Perry Harvey\, Sr. Park 1000 E. Harrison St. Tampa \, FL 33602 Un
 ited States
DESCRIPTION:African Arts in the Park Tampa is a vibrant celebration of Afr
 ican cultural heritage\, showcasing the richness and diversity of African 
 art forms. This festival is dedicated to highlighting an often under-marke
 ted cultural gem of Tampa\, offering both residents and visitors a unique 
 and enriching experience. April 11\, 2026 11:30 am - 9 pm Perry Harvey\, S
 r. Park \n\nPermalink: https://www.tampa.gov/node/187971
